title: GTA 6 Got Leaked Again...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be more footage of Grand Theft Auto 6 before we even get to see anything officially. With Rockstar announcing the trailer for this Tuesday, I'm personally beyond excited to finally play a new game in one of my favourite franchises again. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
